Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:50.92,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&H917477&\fs30\pos(628,373)}我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:50.92,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&H8C6F71&\fs24\pos(906,319)}到底哪里错了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:50.92,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&H8C6F71&\fs24\pos(911,362)}我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:50.92,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5A4140&\fs30\pos(1191,858)}我不太行啊
