Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:06.60,IN_JP_EP03,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}思い込んで慰めてる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.35,IN_JP_EP03,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}見つけたくって
